		<p class="hidden"><?% echo( _('<strong>Typical Security (Default):</strong> Allows all traffic from home network to internet and blocks all unrelated traffic from internet to home network.'));?></p>
		<p class="hidden"><?% echo( _('<strong>Custom security:</strong> Block specific services as per selection.'));?></p>
	</div>
    <div class="module">
